## 🏁 Quick Smoke Test (5 minutes)

Run through this minimal path to verify core flow works:

1. ✅ Products page loads with products
2. ✅ Suppliers page loads with suppliers
3. ✅ Create a PR with a product from the picker → price auto-fills
4. ✅ Submit PR → Approve in Approvals page
5. ✅ Convert to PO → Supplier picker shows availability badges
6. ✅ Submit PO → Approve → Send to Supplier
7. ✅ Supplier portal login → Accept PO
8. ✅ Receive goods on buyer side → Inventory increases
9. ✅ Inventory page shows updated stock
10. ✅ AI Insights page loads with data
